&lt;h1 id="embrace-accountability-to-get-leverage"&gt;Embrace Accountability to Get Leverage&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 11 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take risks under your own name and society will reward you with leverage&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
